column5: How is the water level in Lake of the Woods, compared to last year? Thanks, DS
Water has dropped approx. 6-10" since July 10 but still way above last year. They also got at least 2-4" rain last weekend so would think it's back up. Dennis
Left LOTW yesterday after spending 4 months there. The water level is down from earlier in the year, but still well above last year's low. It is now in the normal range.
